ilias]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：punct（点）+il+ious→（做事）点滴不漏→一丝不苟的"},{"type":"text","text":"punctiiousness（n.一丝不苟，谨小慎微）"},{"type":"entry","text":"deviate","headword":"deviate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.越轨，偏离（to diverge;digress)"},{"type":"text","text":"[di:viert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：de（离开）+vi（道路）+ate→使偏离道路→偏离"},{"type":"text","text":"deviate from 偏离..."},{"type":"entry","text":"encyclopedic","headword":"encyclopedic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj广博的，知识渊博的"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn,sarkla'pi:drk]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：en（进入）+cyclo（圆圈）+ped（儿童教育）+ic→受遍教育→广博的，知"},{"type":"text","text":"识溯博的"},{"type":"entry","text":"staunch","headword":"staunch"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj坚定的，忠诚的（steadfast in loyalty or principle)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sto:nt]"},{"type":"text","text":"constant, inflexible, stalwart, tried-and-true"},{"type":"entry","text":"chauvinistic","headword":"chauvinistic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj沙文主义的，盲目爱国的（excessive or blind patriotism)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fauvr'nrstrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自人名Chauvin，因其过分的爱国主义和对拿破仑的忠诚而闻名"},{"type":"entry","text":"unkempt","headword":"unkempt"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.蓬乱的，未梳理的（notcombed）：不整洁的，乱糖糟的（messy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'kempt]"},{"type":"entry","text":"vacuous","headword":"vacuous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 空虚的，发呆的(marked by lack of ideas or inteligence)"},{"type":"text","text":"[vakjuas]"},{"type":"text","text":"bare, blank, empty, inane, vacant"},{"type":"entry","text":"celebrated","headword":"celebrated"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj有名的，知名的（famous,renowned)"},{"type":"text","text":"['selrbrertrd]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自celebrate（v庆祝，赞扬）"},{"type":"text","text":"be widely celebrated 广泛知名的"}]},{"number":139,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"forge","headword":"forge"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.铁匠铺(smithy)v使形成，达成(to form or shape)：伪造（to counterfeit)：锻制，"},{"type":"text","text":"[f:rd