n","text":"v. 给予(理由)to give as reason or proof);举出(例证(to cite as an example)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'du:s]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ad（加强）+duc（引|导）+e→一再引导→举出"},{"type":"entry","text":"affliction","headword":"affliction"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.折磨，痛苦：痛苦的原因：灾害"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'flrk{n]"}]},{"number":141,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"excoriate","headword":"excoriate"},{"type":"text","text":"剥皮(to strip, scratch, or rub ofthe skin); 严厉批评(to denounce harshly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rks'ko:riert]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ex（使）+cori（皮）+ate→使去皮→剥皮"},{"type":"entry","text":"rattle","headword":"rattle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使发出略咯声(to make a rapid succession of short"},{"type":"text","text":"rattle"},{"type":"text","text":"['raetl]"},{"type":"text","text":"sharp noises); 使慌乱L(to make anxious and cause to"},{"type":"text","text":"lose confidence)"},{"type":"text","text":"园参考rattlesnake（n.响尾蛇）"},{"type":"entry","text":"glean","headword":"glean"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.拾(落穗)(to gather grains left by reapers);收集（材料等)(to gather information"},{"type":"text","text":"[gli:n]"},{"type":"text","text":"or material bit by bit)"},{"type":"text","text":"reap"},{"type":"entry","text":"materialize","headword":"materialize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.赋予形体，使具体化（to represent in material form）：出现（to come into"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma'trrialaxz]"},{"type":"text","text":"existence)"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自material（n.物质acj物质的：具体的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"delegate","headword":"delegate"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 代表(representative)"},{"type":"text","text":"['deligat]"},{"type":"entry","text":"cower","headword":"cower"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 畏缩，蜷缩(to crouch or huddle up from fear or cold)"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：cow（威胁）+er→受到威胁→畏缩，蜷缩"},{"type":"text","text":"['kauar]"},{"type":"entry","text":"squelch","headword":"squelch"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 压制,镇压(to completely suppress; quell)"},{"type":"text","text":"[skwelt]]"},{"type":"text","text":"图squelcharumour/strike/fire制止谣言；镇压罢工；控制火势蔓延"},{"type":"entry","text":"list","headword":"list"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 倾舒斜(to tilt to one side) n. 倾斜"},{"type":"text","text":"[lrst]"},{"type":"text","text":"list意义很多，常见的有“名单，列表”→列表要摆放整齐，不能倾斜"},{"type":"entry","text":"testimony","headword":"testimony"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 证据, 证词](firsthand authentication of a fact; evidence)"},{"type":"text","text":"['testimauni]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：testi（证据）+mony→证据"},{"type":"text","text":"The testimony of eyewitnesses is notoriously unreliable; emotion and"},{"type":"text","text":"excitemenit all too often cause our minds to distort what we see."},{"type":"entry","text":"scads","headword":"scads"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.许多，巨额(large numbers or amounts)"},{"type":"text","text":"[skaedz]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈scadsof大量，许多"},{"type":"entry","text":"measured","headword":"measured"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj量过的，精确的(determined by measurement)：慎重的，恰如其分的(careful,"},{"type":"text","text":"['mezard]"},{"type":"text","text":"restrained)"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自measure（v测量）"},{"type":"entry","text":"puerile","headword":"puerile"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj幼稚的(immature);孩子气的(juvenile)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pjural]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：puer（男孩）+ile→孩子气的"},{"type":"entry","text":"mollify","headword":"mollify"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 安慰, 安抚(to soften in feeling or temper; appease)"},{"type":"text","text":"['ma:lrfar]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：moll（柔软的）+ify→使柔软→安抚"}]},{"number":142,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 11 >>>"},{"type":"text","text":"Science progresses by building on what has come before; important findings"},{"type":"text","text":"thus form the basis of subsequent experiments."},{"type":"entry","text":"execrate","headword":"execrate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 增恶(to loathe; detest; abhor): 咒写(to call down evil upon; Curse)"},{"type":"text","text":"['eksikrert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ex（出）+ecr（看作secr，神圣的）+ate→走出了神圣→咒骂"},{"type":"entry","text":"majestic","headword":"majestic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj雄伟的，庄严的（showing majesty)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ma'd3estrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：maj（大的）+estic→雄伟的"},{"type":"text","text":"The eradlication of pollution is not merely a matter of aesthetics, though the"},{"type":"text","text":"majestic beauty of nature is indeed an important consideration."},{"type":"entry","text":"implicit","headword":"implicit"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj含蓄的，暗示的（not directly expressed)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xm'plrsrt]"},{"type":"text","text":"围词根记忆：im（使）+plic(重叠）+it→（意义）叠在里面→含蓄的"},{"type":"entry","text":"dour","headword":"dour"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj严厉的，阴郁的，倔强的（sullen, gloomy, stubborn)"},{"type":"text","text":"['dauar]"},{"type":"text","text":"glum, moody, morose, saturnine, sour, sulky"},{"type":"entry","text":"prowess","headword":"prowess"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.勇数(distinguished bravery);非凡的才能(extraordinary ability)"},{"type":"text","text":"['prauas]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自prow（aoj.[古]英勇的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"sententious","headword":"sententious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 说教的(abounding in excessive moralizing);简要的(terse, pithy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sen'tenfas]"},{"type":"text","text":"国联想记忆：sentence（句子）+tious→一句话说完→简要的"},{"type":"entry","text":"omniscient","headword":"omniscient"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj无所不知的，博识的（knowing allthings)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a:m'nrsiant]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：omni（全）+sci（知道）+ent→全知道的→无所不知的"},{"type":"entry","text":"multifarious","headword":"multifarious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj多种的，各式各样的(numerous and varied)"},{"type":"text","text":"[mAltr'ferias]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：multi（多）+fari（部分）+ous→含有许多部分的→多种多样的"},{"type":"entry","text":"gourmet","headword":"gourmet"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 美食家(a person who is an excellent judge of fine foods and drinks)"},{"type":"text","text":"['gurmer]"},{"type":"text","text":"园注意与gourmand的不同：gourmand指贪吃的人，而gourmet指品尝食品是否"},{"type":"text","text":"美味的人"},{"type":"entry","text":"engaging","headword":"engaging"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.迷人的，美丽动人的(tending to draw favorable attention)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rn'gerdzin]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自engage（v吸引l）"},{"type":"entry","text":"felicitous","headword":"felicitous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. (话语等)适当的，得体的(used or expressed in a way suitable to the occasion;"},{"type":"text","text":"[fa'lisrtas]"},{"type":"text","text":"appropriate)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：felic（幸福的）+itous→（讲话）使人幸福的→得体的"},{"type":"entry","text":"vague","headword":"vague"},{"type":"text","text":"[verg]"},{"type":"text","text":"form, or character; indistinct)"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：vag（漫游）+ue→思路四处漫游→含期的；模糊的"}]},{"number":143,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"enliven","headword":"enliven"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使--更活跃或更愉快(to make sb./sth.more lively or cheerful)"},{"type":"text","text":"[In'laivn]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：en（使）+live（充满活动的，令人愉快的）+n→使更活跃或更愉快"},{"type":"entry","text":"pressing","headword":"pressing"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 紧迫的，迫切的(urgently important);悬切要求的(asking for sth. strongly)"},{"type":"text","text":"['presin]"},{"type":"entry","text":"dissemble","headword":"dissemble"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.假装，掩饰（感情、意图等）（to conceal;disguise）"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'sembl]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：dis（不）+semble（相同）→不和（本来面目）相同→掩饰"},{"type":"entry","text":"associate","headword":"associate"},{"type":"text","text":"[a’sauJiat] adj. 联合的(joined) n. 合伙人(partner, colleague)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'saufiert]v使发生联系，使联合（tojoin people or things together)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：as（加强）+soci（同伴，引申为“社会”）+ate→成为社团→联合的"},{"type":"entry","text":"resourceful","headword":"resourceful"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 机智的(good at finding ways to deal with difficult situations)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr's:rsfl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：和resource（n.资源）一起记"},{"type":"entry","text":"persistence","headword":"persistence"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.坚持不懈，执意，持续(the quality or state of being persistent)"},{"type":"text","text":"来自persist（v.坚持，持续，固执）"},{"type":"text","text":"[par'sistans]"},{"type":"text","text":"Contrary to the popular conception that it is powered"},{"type":"text","text":"by conscious objectivity, science often operates through"},{"type":"text","text":"disguise"},{"type":"text","text":"error, happy accidents, hunches and persistence in spite"},{"type":"text","text":"of mistakes."},{"type":"entry","text":"husband","headword":"husband"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 节省，节约(to manage prudently and economically)"},{"type":"text","text":"['hAzband]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：丈夫（husband）省钱(husband)"},{"type":"entry","text":"flaccid","headword":"flaccid"},{"type":"text","text":"aoj. 松弛的(soft and limply flabby);软弱的(weak, feeble)"},{"type":"text","text":"['flaesrd]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：flac（看作flab，松的）+cid→松弛的"},{"type":"text","text":"cluster"},{"type":"entry","text":"pretext","headword":"pretext"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 借 口(a purpose or motive assumed in order to cloak the real intention)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pri:tekst]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pre（预先）+text（文章）→预先想好的文章→借口"},{"type":"entry","text":"univocal","headword":"univocal"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 单—意思的(having only one meaning)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ju:'nrvakl]"},{"type":"text","text":"univocal concept 单一概念"}]},{"number":144,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 11 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"fury","headword":"fury"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.狂怒，狂暴（intense，disordered rage）：激烈，猛烈：狂怒的人（one who"},{"type":"text","text":"[f3:ri]"},{"type":"text","text":"resembles an avenging spirit); (希腊神话中的)复仇女神(the Furies goddesses in"},{"type":"text","text":"Greek mythology)"},{"type":"entry","text":"boo","headword":"boo"},{"type":"definition","text":"v发出嘘声int.（表示不满，轻蔗等）嘘"},{"type":"text","text":"[bu:]"},{"type":"text","text":"园发音记忆：“不”→发出嘘声"},{"type":"text","text":"dispose"},{"type":"entry","text":"dispose","headword":"dispose"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使倾向于：处理(to give a tendency to: to settle a matter"},{"type":"text","text":"[dt'spauz]"},{"type":"text","text":"finally)"},{"type":"text","text":"dispose of 去掉，清除"},{"type":"entry","text":"vaporize","headword":"vaporize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. (使）蒸发(to convert or be converted into vapor)"},{"type":"text","text":"['veiparaiz]"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自vapor（n.蒸汽）"},{"type":"text","text":"Despite the mixture's volatile nature, we found that by lowering its temperature"},{"type":"text","text":"in the laboratory we could dramatically reduce its tendency to vaporize."},{"type":"entry","text":"taciturn","headword":"taciturn"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 沉默寡言的(temperamentally disinclined to talk)"},{"type":"text","text":"['taesrtsirn]"},{"type":"text","text":"mute, reserved, reticent, withdrawn"},{"type":"text","text":"taciturnity（n.沉默寡言）"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.倾斜 n.斜面(a slanting direction)：观点(a peculiar or personal point of view)"},{"type":"entry","text":"slant","headword":"slant"},{"type":"text","text":"[slaent]"},{"type":"entry","text":"proclaim","headword":"proclaim"},{"type":"definition","text":"v宣告，公布（to declare officially);显示，表明(to show clearly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pra'klerm]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：pro（在前）+claim（叫，喊）→在前面减→宣告，公布"},{"type":"entry","text":"meddle","headword":"meddle"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.干涉，干预（to interfere)"},{"type":"text","text":"['medl]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：med（中间）+dle→在中间干涉→干涉"},{"type":"entry","text":"illuminate","headword":"illuminate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 阐明，解释(to make understandable);照亮(to brighten"},{"type":"text","text":"illuminate"},{"type":"text","text":"[x'lu:minert]"},{"type":"text","text":"with lights)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：i（向内）+lumin（光）+ate→投入光→照亮"},{"type":"text","text":"Since most if not all learning occurs through"},{"type":"text","text":"comparisons, relating one observation to another, it would"},{"type":"text","text":"be strange indeed if the study of other cultures did not"},{"type":"text","text":"also illuminare the study of our own."},{"type":"entry","text":"eternal","headword":"eternal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 永久的，永恒的(without beginning or end)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r't3:rnl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：外部（external)世界是永恒的（eternal）诱惑"}]},{"number":145,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"text","text":"B In sharp contrast to the intense idealism of the young republic, with its utopian"},{"type":"text","text":"faith in democracy and hopes for eternal human progress, recent developments"},{"type":"text","text":"suggest a mood of almost unrelieved cynicism."},{"type":"entry","text":"parley","headword":"parley"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 和谈(a conference with an enemy);会谈(a conference for discussion of"},{"type":"text","text":"['pa:rli]"},{"type":"text","text":"points in dispute) v 和谈，会谈(to speak with another)"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：parl（讲话）+ey→会谈"},{"type":"entry","text":"dire","headword":"dire"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 可怕的(dreadful, miserable)"},{"type":"text","text":"['darar]"},{"type":"text","text":"appalling, fearful, formidiable, frightful, ghastly, tremendous"},{"type":"entry","text":"apt","headword":"apt"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.易于-的：恰当的"},{"type":"text","text":"[aept]"},{"type":"text","text":"be apt to容易..的；很可能"},{"type":"text","text":"图aptness（n.倾向：才能）"},{"type":"entry","text":"hoax","headword":"hoax"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.骗局，恶作剧(a trick or fraud) v欺骗(to deceive;cheat)"},{"type":"text","text":"[hauks]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：不要和coax（v哄骗）混淆"},{"type":"entry","text":"arrest","headword":"arrest"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.逮捕：阻止，制止(to stop or check)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'rest]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ar（加强）+rest（休息）→强制休息→速捕"},{"type":"text","text":"arrest"},{"type":"text","text":"arresting（adj.醒目的，引l人注意的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"pandemonium","headword":"pandemonium"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.喧器，大混乱(a wild uproar;tumult)"},{"type":"text","text":"[penda'mauniam]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：pan（全部）+demon（魔鬼）+ium→全是魔鬼"},{"type":"text","text":"→大混乱：来自弥尔顿的著作《失乐园》中的地狱之都"},{"type":"text","text":"(Pandemonium)"},{"type":"entry","text":"exhaustive","headword":"exhaustive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 御底的，无遗漏的(covering every possible detail;thorough)"},{"type":"text","text":"[1g'zistrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"an exhaustive report 详尽的报告"},{"type":"entry","text":"disclose","headword":"disclose"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 揭露 (to allow sth. to be seen; reveal)"},{"type":"text","text":"[drs'klauz]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：dis（不）+close（关闭）→不再关闭→揭露"},{"type":"entry","text":"square","headword":"square"},{"type":"definition","text":"V. —致, 符合(to be or make sth. consistent with sth.:;"},{"type":"text","text":"penalty迟到五次"},{"type":"text","text":"[skwer]"},{"type":"text","text":"agree with); 结清(to balance)"},{"type":"text","text":"奖金全扣"},{"type":"text","text":"square up 清算账目"},{"type":"entry","text":"penalty","headword":"penalty"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 刑罚, 处罚(punishment for breaking a law or contract)"},{"type":"text","text":"l'penaltij]"},{"type":"definition","text":"A major goal of law, to deter potential criminals by"},{"type":"text","text":"punishing wrongdoers, is not served when the penalty is"},{"type":"text","text":"so seldom invoked that it ceases to be a credible threat."},{"type":"entry","text":"jettison","headword":"jettison"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.(船等）向外抛弃货物（to cast overboard off)n.抛弃的货物（jetsam）n.抛弃（action"},{"type":"text","text":"['dzetisn]"},{"type":"text","text":"of throwing)"}]},{"number":146,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 11 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"shoddy","headword":"shoddy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.劣质的，假冒的（cheaply imitative)"},{"type":"text","text":"['fa:di]"},{"type":"text","text":"second-rate"},{"type":"entry","text":"condign","headword":"condign"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.罪有应得的(of punishment) severe and well deserved);适宜的"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'darn]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：con（表加强）+dign（高贵）→惩罚罪行，弘扬高贵→罪有应得的"},{"type":"entry","text":"culmination","headword":"culmination"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.顶点;高潮(eventual conclusion or result)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,kAlmr'nex{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自culminate（v达到顶点）"},{"type":"entry","text":"patent","headword":"patent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.显而易见的（readily visible;obvious)n.专利权（证书)"},{"type":"text","text":"['paetnt]"},{"type":"text","text":"Copyright and patent laws attempt to encourage innovation by ensuring that"},{"type":"text","text":"inventors are paid for creative work, so it would be ironic if expanded protection"},{"type":"text","text":"under these laws dliscouraged entrepreneurial innovation by increasing fears of"},{"type":"text","text":"lawsuits."},{"type":"entry","text":"forswear","headword":"forswear"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.管绝，发警放弃(to renounce on oath)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fo:r'swer]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：for（否定）+swear（发誓）→否定誓言→誓绝"},{"type":"entry","text":"animate","headword":"animate"},{"type":"text","text":"[aenrmat] adfj.活的，有生命的(alive,having life)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aenrmert] v 赋予生命(to give life to)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：anim（生命，精神）+ate→有生命的：赋予生命"},{"type":"text","text":"animated (adj. 活生生的，生动的);inanimate （adj. 无生命的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"prominent","headword":"prominent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 显著的(noticeable);著名的(widely and popularly known)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pra:minant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pro（向前）+min（伸出）+ent→向前伸出→显著的；著名的"},{"type":"entry","text":"inchoate","headword":"inchoate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj刚开始的(just begun; incipient);未充分发展的，不成熟的(not yet completed"},{"type":"text","text":"[In'kauat]"},{"type":"text","text":"or fully developed)"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：inch（英寸）+oat（燕麦）+e→燕麦刚长了一英寸→未充分发展的，不成"},{"type":"text","text":"熟的"},{"type":"entry","text":"covert","headword":"covert"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj秘密的，隐蔽的(concealed,hidden)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kauv3:rt]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：cover（遮盖）+t→盖住的→秘密的"},{"type":"entry","text":"flair","headword":"flair"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.天赋，本领，天资（a natural talent or ability)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fler]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：和fair（adj.公正的：美丽的）一起记"},{"type":"entry","text":"disavow","headword":"disavow"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.否认，否定，抵赖(to say one does not know of, is not responsible for, or does"},{"type":"text","text":"[disa'vau]"},{"type":"text","text":"not approve of)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：dis（不）+avow（承认）→不承认→否认，否定"},{"type":"text","text":"图disavowal (n. 否认)"},{"type":"entry","text":"polemical","headword":"polemical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj引|起争论的，好解的(controversial; disputatious)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pa'lemxkl]"}]},{"number":147,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"neophyte","headword":"neophyte"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.初学者，新手(a beginner or a novice)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ni:afart]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：neo（新的）+phyt（植物）+e→新长的植物→新手"},{"type":"entry","text":"betoken","headword":"betoken"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.预示，表示（to signily:indicate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[br'taukan]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：be（使）+token（记号，标志）→使成为标志→预示"},{"type":"entry","text":"ancillary","headword":"ancillary"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 辅助的(subordinate,auxiliary) n.助手(aid)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aensaleri]"},{"type":"text","text":"forgo"},{"type":"entry","text":"forgo","headword":"forgo"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.放弃，抛弃(to abstain from; give up; relinquish)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fs:rgau]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：for（为了）+go（走）→为了寻求新事物而出去一"},{"type":"text","text":"放弃"},{"type":"entry","text":"labyrinth","headword":"labyrinth"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 迷宫(a maze formed by paths separated by high hedges);错综复杂"},{"type":"text","text":"['laebarine]"},{"type":"text","text":"(something extremely complex or tortuous)"},{"type":"text","text":"labyrinthine （adj迷宫的;复杂的）"}]}]}